(12, 'Benefits Administrator', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0', '', 648506, '', 'both', '', '', '<p>Benefits Administrator Assistant</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Administrative Assistant is the front-line support for our clients, their employees, insurance carrier personnel and vendors. The position requires exemplarily communication skills, excellent customer service abilities, problem solving, follow-up and a sense of urgency. The position is responsible for verbal and written employee communication and distribution to our clients. To be successful, you will need to be self-motivated, a self-starter, have a sense of urgency and be a continuous learner.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div>\r\n			<p>&nbsp; About Us</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><!--[endif]----></p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"left\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td height=\"5\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"Text Box:   About Us\" height=\"33\" src=\"file:///C:/Users/Owner/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.png\" width=\"282\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a small company working in a very complex industry. We operate wit a modest staff, deliver a top-quality product while taking a leadership position in the adaption of industry changes. We accomplish this trough technology, education, and industry foresight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div>\r\n			<p>&nbsp; Daily Activities</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</