(26, 'Senior Property Restoration Consultant ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '55000', '', 582069, '', 'both', '', '', '<div>\r\n<div>Senior Property Restoration Estimator</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Skills Set Needed:&nbsp;Senior level experience in commercial large construction property restoration , IICRC Certifications, Xactimate Software proficiency, Excellent estimate skills and good command on how to manipulate the software. Out of this world people skills, excellent computer proficiency, excellent written and verbal skills, excellent time management skills, stellar professional ethics and ability to have compassion with the clients.&nbsp; YOU STAND IN THE GAP BETWEEN DISASTER AND BEING MADE WHOLE AGAIN! act like you realize this.&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Location of home office is Kennesaw Georgia but be prepared to travel around Georgia and beyond if necessary!</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Compensation - Market level compensation and more if you are above the normal grade estimator .&nbsp; Excellent Medical insurance/vacation/PTO/LTD/STD/ and so much more. You will be provided with a list of benefits and additional options for you</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Property restoration, exactimate software, construction, Supervisory role,managing crews', 27209, 0, '0', '0', '', '', 0, '2018-09-10 10:36:48', 0, 300, 110);

